# Scratchpad - Font Verification Task

## Checklist
- [x] Navigate to http://localhost:8000
- [x] Take screenshot of login/onboarding screen
- [x] Click "Demo mode" button if available
- [x] Verify Baloo 2 font is used for application text
- [x] Take screenshot of main page
- [x] Report visual appearance and verify kid-friendliness

## Findings
- **Font Verification:** The entire application (both login/onboarding and the main dashboard) correctly renders all text using the **Baloo 2** font family.
- **Kid-Friendliness:** The font is highly rounded, soft, and playful. This makes it perfect for children, giving a friendly, non-intimidating, and game-like vibe.
- **Vietnamese Support:** The font renders all Vietnamese diacritics beautifully and correctly (e.g., "Chế Độ Demo", "Rồng Demo", "Khu Vườn", "Nhiệm Vụ", "Xếp Hạng", "Bạn Bè").
- **Overall UI:** The layout looks extremely neat and visually appealing with a dark theme and colorful indicators (HP red/pink, Vui yellow/orange, NL blue).


